Overview
--------

The OpenSSO OAuth Token Service supports OAuth Core 1.0 spec in terms 
of OAuth token management, including OAuth consumer registration,
OAuth request token management/authorization, and OAuth access
token management. The OpenSSO OAuth Token Service is embedded with 
the OpenSSO server. 


OAuth Token Service URLs
------------------------

Consumer Registration/Deletion URL:
http(s)://host:port/deploy-uri/oauth/index.jsp

Request Token URL: 
http(s)://host:port/deploy-uri/resources/1/oauth/get_request_token

Request Token Authorization URL: 
http(s)://host:port/deploy-uri/oauth/userconsole.jsp

Access Token URL: 
http(s)://host:port/deploy-uri/resources/1/oauth/get_access_token


OAuth Token Service Samples
---------------------------
The samples for the OAuth Token Service are located in samples 
subdirectory. Please refer to its README file for details.

